parameters: I can't leave this place just yet.
I can't leave this place just yet.
I can't leave this place just yet.
Ok!\! We saw the mansion, it’s super creepy.\! Can we go b-back?
Creepy?\! Apart from dirt and dust this mansion is just a big empty ol’ house.
Why are you guys so scared of ghosts?\! Isn’t Hildr technically one?
Kyaaaaaaaa!!!\! Take that and that and this you stupid ghosts!
Oh...\! That voice, I just recognized it...
I knew you would fail your mission, Thalia.\! I waited here for your incompetence
to drive them to my mansion~
Thalia!\! I knew you were plotting something!
No, wait, Hildr!\! You have to believe me, I’ve turned a new leaf!
HAH!\! As if she would be capable of such a plan.
You seem to be the only beauty with wits here~
Tremble in fear and kneel!\! I am \w[60] Carmen Maria Antonieta Pujols Salomé Hortensia
Rosalía Paula Josefina Angelina de Sara Fausta Teresa Isabel Yolanda Gabriela
Fernanda Franchesca Hortensia Gavarras Santa de los Arroyos Blancos de la Fálica
Psst...\! Master, use your first and literal last name.
NONSENSE!\! I am PROUD of my names!\! All 28 of them!
I am Carmen Fabergas!\! Proud descendant of the prestigious Fálica Familia Dracónica.
Shut your mouth!\! I will not have you disrespect me!
M-my magic!\! I can’t summon my thunder!
\WaveOhohohoho!\! \ResetShakeThe moment you walked into my illustrious mansion, you sealed your fates!\! The entire
perimeter is one giant magic seal, a very high level one.
For an illustrious mansion, it’s pretty dusty.
We don’t really do a good job, to be honest.
Enough!\! I’ll lock you girls up until Ursula arrives!
As for you...\! How do I put this...\! I have different plans~
I hate to admit it, but upon first glance at you...\! I am terribly infatuated...
You might be a...little too mature looking for me.\! I have a solution for that, though.\!
Master Carmen is a bit of a-
I need to be careful next time...
I need to be careful next time...
Gotta say...\! It's nice to have you back in full size and smell...
Roz-chan, Lady Hildr, and red thing...\! Apologies for my behavior unbecoming of the head of my family.
Why am I red thing?\! I'm a person and my name is Thalia!
No worries.\! I'm just glad we could talk it out.
Carmen, I have something to ask you.
Why can't you tell us?\! Have you not turned a new leaf?
Just because I am no longer on Ursula's side, doesn't mean I switched over to yours.
That means you're not on MY side...?
She's looking for a source of mana.\! Though she didn't divulge a whole lot of information
to me.\! I merely rallied to her.
The Master and us had nothing better to do, so this is welcome entertainment.
\ShakeWould really be great if you could stop spooking us like that...
Sorry, it's fun for us to startle you.
You...\! I'll have a word with you and your sisters.
Yes, master.\! Please spank us for our bad behavior.
D-don't make me sound like a pervert!!
Ahem.\! Allow me to walk all of you to the entrance.
Kaaaaakakaka!\! So you worms have failed me!
You little wench.\! You had one job, yet you failed.
I feel an intense aura coming from her...
Carmen, you worthless maggot.\! You are truly unworthy of being called a dragon.
Shut up and settle down!\! I’m not done talking!!
Huh?\! My magic is sealed again!\! Thalia, dispel it!
Yawn...\! How about I teach you a lesson.
Tch...\! So you mastered that, huh?
In any case, I severed your mana channels.\! You are no longer a threat to me or to
You’re no more threatening than a puppy.
Let's put you all out of your misery then.
Tch.\! Whatever, it’s not like you’d let me kill them.
I have better things to do.\! Once I find the source of mana, that shield of yours won’t
be able to save you.\! I’ll rip each and every one of you apart.
Be good little children and stay put ok?\! Kaaaaaaaaaaakakakakaka!
